title: ID_Object_MaryLighter_Collected_ENG
tag: EventFlags.Mary.Dialogues.AtHome.Completed
---
Daniel: (<i>Thinking about it, that looks like a lighter. It's ornated with some letters, maybe the initials of the owner.</i>) #tone:thinking
Daniel: (<i>A lighter under the bed of a man died in a fire. Mmh...</i>) #tone:thinking
Daniel: (<i>I'm starting to doubt it merely "fell" here.</i>) #tone:serious
Daniel: (<i>I need to talk to Mary.</i>) #tone:serious
<<SetTag EventFlags.MaryLighter.PickedUp true>>
===
//FINE


title: ID_Object_ToiletPaper_Seen_ENG
---
