---
Daniel: (<i>It's not really believable that the lighter was found on the crime scene.</i>) #tone:thinking
Daniel: (<i>It should be dented, or dinged. I need to find a way to ruin it.</i>) #tone:serious
Daniel: (<i>Mmh... Maybe cake isn't the only thing paper towels are useful for.</i>) #tone:serious
